\par\plain \ilvl0{\listtext	\f0\fs26\b0\i0 \uc0\u8259 	}{\f0\fs26\b0\i0 I will sometimes use embedded instructions within a narrative or dialogue marker. These instructions will help you write dialogue tags action tags, or guide you in writing the narrative. I will place the embedded instructions between the label and the \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93:\u8221\'94.}
